## Why Choose Claude?

Claude excels at long-text processing and professional writing, making it ideal for business documents, reports, and formal emails.

## Writing Business Reports

### Provide Clear Structure Requirements
Tell Claude the target audience, core topic, and expected chapter structure of the report.

### Write in Sections
For long reports, have Claude write chapter by chapter, focusing on one section at a time to ensure quality.

## Writing Professional Emails

### Template Approach
Provide Claude with the email scenario, recipient information, and your core message to generate a professional draft.

### Tone Adjustment
By specifying the tone (formal, friendly, urgent, etc.), ensure the email style matches the situation.

## Document Polishing

Hand your draft to Claude and ask it to:
1. Check grammar and spelling errors
2. Optimize sentence structure and expression
3. Ensure logical flow
4. Maintain a professional yet readable style

## Tips

- Provide specific examples and references for better results
- Iterate: generate a first draft, then refine based on feedback
- Always verify the accuracy of AI-generated content
